name: Keyboard Master (Supereiris)
description:
How good do you know the positions of the keys in your keyboard? Do you have the muscle memory needed to press them with out looking?

Keyboard Master offers you a way to test your skills and become the best of the best - the KEYBOARD MASTER

.

.

.

I made this game to test out  LootLocker's leaderboards which turn out to be really useful and easy to make.

Credits:

  • Art assets and some sound effects by me
  • Font:  Symtext
  • Background music by joshuaempyre
  • Hit sound effect by OwlStorm
  • Leaderboard by LootLocker

Thanks for playing!
